OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FP&O Ferries says it didn't 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbreak law over sackings    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, P&O Ferries has denied suggestions that
OL,6, it broke the law when it sacked 800    
OL,7, workers without warning last week.     
OL,9,FMinisters had questioned whether the   
OL,10,Fmove was legal under British law - but 
OL,11,Fin a letter, the firm said those       
OL,12,Faffected were employed outside the UK. 
OL,14,FIt also said staff would benefit from a
OL,15,F#36.5m redundancy pot - with around 40 
OL,16,Fgetting more than #100,000 each.       
OL,18,FUnions said the compensation package   
OL,19,Fbeing offered was "pure blackmail and  
OL,20,Fthreats".                              
